Installation Instructions
-------------------------

Dependencies:
    - A Perl 5 interpreter
    - Package DBD::SQLite3 (provided by libdbd-sqlite3-perl on Debian systems)
    - sqlite3-pcre (available in many distro repositories, if not, go to
        https://github.com/ralight/sqlite3-pcre and download it. Run 'make'
        and 'sudo make install' on the unzipped version of it.
    - Package Tk (provided by perl-tk on Debian systems)

To install to the system path:
    - Ensure you have met all dependency requirements.
    - Run the install script in install_linux.sh or install_win.bat,
      depending on your operating system.

To run:
    Type bookdblite in the command-line. It should then run as expected.
